data.description:
Odaily Planet Daily News According to @lookonchain monitoring, before Base officially released the "Base is for everyone" token-related tweet, 3 wallets bought a large number of tokens in advance and then sold them, making a total profit of about $666,000.
Address 0x0992 used 1.5 ETH (about $2,370) to purchase 256 million tokens, and sold them for 108 ETH (about $170,000), making a profit of about $168,000;
Address 0x5D9D used 1 ETH to purchase 82.86 million tokens, and sold them for 169.7 ETH (about $267,600), making a profit of about $266,000;
Address 0xBD31 used 1 ETH to purchase 132 million tokens, and sold 110 million of them for a profit of about $231,800.
